title: Confinement Feeding Operations Registered with the Iowa DNR, Iowa, 2008
name: Confinement Feeding Operations Registered with the Iowa DNR, Iowa, 2008
description:
Purpose:
    This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources. 
Supplemental_Information:
    This coverage supplants the CAFOs coverage, due to the legal definition for CAFO meaning only facilities with 1000 animal units or more. 
Abstract:
    This file contains locations of confinement feeding operations that are registered with the Iowa DNR.
